metadata.name: Order of the Occult #1
metadata.description: Enter a world shrouded in mystery and dark magic, featuring a coven of powerful occultists who hold the secrets of the universe in their grasp. Each intricately designed token is a portal into a realm of hidden knowledge and arcane power, where the ancient forces of good and evil clash in a timeless battle for supremacy. Unleash the hidden potential within yourself as you join the ranks of these mystical adepts, and unlock the secrets of the universe that have been hidden from humanity for centuries. The power is within your grasp - will you dare to claim it?
